PRIVACY POLICY — Tik Tok Follower Tracker Live

Effective Date: May 7, 2026
Last Updated: May 7, 2026

1. INTRODUCTION

Tik Tok Follower Tracker Live ("we", "our", or "the app") is an independent third-party application developed for entertainment and informational purposes. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our app.

We are committed to protecting your privacy. This app is designed with a privacy-first approach — we do not require you to create an account, log in, or provide any personal information to use the app.

2. INFORMATION WE DO NOT COLLECT

We do NOT collect, store, or process:

Your name, email address, or any personal identifier
Your TikTok account credentials or passwords
Your location data
Your device contacts or photos
Any financial or payment information
3. INFORMATION COLLECTED AUTOMATICALLY

a) Usage Data via Google AdMob
Our app displays advertisements powered by Google AdMob. AdMob may automatically collect certain information to serve relevant ads, including:

Device type and operating system version
Advertising ID (Google Advertising ID / GAID)
App usage and interaction data
IP address (used to determine general location for ad targeting)
This data is collected and processed by Google in accordance with Google's Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy

You can opt out of personalized advertising by adjusting your device settings:
Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization

b) Crash Reports
If the app crashes, anonymous crash data may be collected by the Android operating system or Google Play Services to help us improve stability. This data does not identify you personally.

4. HOW WE USE TIKTOK DATA

When you search for a TikTok username, the app fetches publicly available profile information (follower count, likes, following count, video count, display name, and profile picture) from a third-party data service.

We do NOT store this data on any server we operate
We do NOT link this data to your identity
Searched usernames and profile data are stored locally on your device only (in the Track History feature) and never transmitted to us
You can clear your Track History at any time from within the app
5. LOCAL STORAGE (ON-DEVICE ONLY)

The app stores the following data locally on your device:

A list of TikTok usernames you have previously tracked (Track History)
The last known follower count for each tracked profile
This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us. You can delete it by clearing the app's data or uninstalling the app.

6. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

This app uses the following third-party services which have their own privacy policies:

Service	Purpose	Privacy Policy
Google AdMob	Advertising	https://policies.google.com/privacy
Google Play Services	App distribution & crash reporting	https://policies.google.com/privacy
We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party services.

7. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

This app is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information through our app, please contact us and we will take steps to delete such information.

8. DATA SECURITY

Since we do not collect or transmit your personal data to our servers, there is no risk of your personal data being compromised through our systems. All locally stored data on your device is protected by your device's built-in security mechanisms.

9. YOUR RIGHTS

Since we do not collect personal data, there is nothing for us to delete, modify, or export on your behalf. All locally stored app data can be removed by:

Clearing app data: Settings → Apps → Tik Tok Follower Tracker Live → Clear Data
Uninstalling the app
10. CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected with an updated "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

11. DISCLAIMER

Tik Tok Follower Tracker Live is an independent third-party application and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or associated with TikTok or ByteDance Ltd. in any way. All TikTok profile data displayed in the app is publicly available information.
